{"tid":1027084,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇籃球撚同足球撚咁水火不容？","createTime":"2019-02-18T14:30:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T17:00:59.000Z","uid":185222,"like":33,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"35cfaad2fb39c0e74100bb45d08bcd2c4ea84dff","tid":1027084,"uid":185222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T14:30:49.000Z","msg":"平心而論 足球同籃球性質 規則 打法都唔一樣 根本就係兩種運動黎 究竟有乜好比？ 點樣比？ <br />\n睇到隔離post籃球撚用籃球同足球嘅price去黎比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇完真係得淡笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又聽過足球撚用球場嘅大細黎比較 話咩足球場大過籃球場幾倍 所以足球撚嘅體力&gt;籃球撚etc... 又或者一尾淨係識講籃球=細路仔玩具 但又無比到咩實際具體嘅解釋點解籃球=細路仔玩具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你照你咁講乒乓波夠係縮細版嘅網球啦 又唔見乒乓波撚同網球撚喺度互屌？<br />\n既然你鍾意得足球/籃球 點解就唔可以對其他運動都比番啲尊重？ 想籃球撚同足球撚唔好再抬高自己 貶低對方真係咁難？<br />\n申利 打開籃球 但從來無睇唔起/貶低足球<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樓主講得岩 籃球撚同足球撚應該互相尊重<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想籃球撚同足球撚和平共處？ 等下世啦"},{"pid":"7c56e337b6aeb6a2d9709fa24c0a9af6bc458ecc","tid":1027084,"uid":68026,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T14:31:54.000Z","msg":"上連登 勿認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"642df7b9c3a02b55bff6b83892d3f71fce8ccd0a","tid":1027084,"uid":206244,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T14:32:11.000Z","msg":"班兒登仔踩其他運動令自己睇落高人一等，其實好撚低賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db181714be047c14bff60e13bcd127f5a384096b","tid":1027084,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T14:37:47.000Z","msg":"籃波足波both toys"},{"pid":"de9efcc356f01dcc94656077fcca010a29028995","tid":1027084,"uid":68457,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T14:39:11.000Z","msg":"老實 我從未聽過兩種運動互踩<br />\n細個無論學校定身邊朋友圈子都無出現過<br />\n唯獨上連燈先第一次見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />簡直大開眼界"},{"pid":"02610b925b47670c83313232597b1426c410a844","tid":1027084,"uid":101110,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T14:45:46.000Z","msg":"其實即係麻甩佬(足球撚)同Mk仔(籃球撚)之爭<br />\n當然都係一碌鳩打一船人<br />\n<br />\n笑吓咪算，但真係有真心膠當真"},{"pid":"caa17efb04ad3c91974271d9a6a9c4c826614166","tid":1027084,"uid":185222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"02610b925b47670c83313232597b1426c410a844","tid":1027084,"uid":101110,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T14:45:46.000Z","msg":"其實即係麻甩佬(足球撚)同Mk仔(籃球撚)之爭<br />\n當然都係一碌鳩打一船人<br />\n<br />\n笑吓咪算，但真係有真心膠當真"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T14:55:49.000Z","msg":"我都想笑下就算 但當我睇到咁多低質又無營養嘅cm先不禁有感而發<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eeacf31e0641dce8aa333c441e673d6bc99caf3","tid":1027084,"uid":60409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T14:57:40.000Z","msg":"上連登 勿認真"},{"pid":"f1db983d9b2ea8a678a6ec51aad8eb194cf10c5b","tid":1027084,"uid":62841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T15:01:03.000Z","msg":"波台狗鳩嗡咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b322ed8c0b8b6ad14a934db441fd6d884ce22c92","tid":1027084,"uid":49062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T15:17:23.000Z","msg":"唔撩事鬥非學咩人做波台狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dae7ae50788bf9a08d908abdeefd9fef6201da9","tid":1027084,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T16:45:03.000Z","msg":"波台狗鳩up引戰，食下花生或者做下假膠就得"},{"pid":"205d500c19c70446ac34d22d063b45587140a5a6","tid":1027084,"uid":9997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T17:00:59.000Z","msg":"籃球生得唔夠高就玩唔到，<br />\n足球就算生得唔高都可以係頂級球員"}]}